# Tax-sale toolkit data (see tax_sale/RUNBOOK-2027.md to regenerate locally):
# - data/probe/   : downloaded MODL public PDFs (large; re-scrapeable)
# - data/raw/     : alternative scrape destination per spec §4
# - data/enrichment/ : manually-collected PVSC values (PII-light but personal)
# - hand-OCR'd JSON fixtures contain real bidder names from MODL's award
#   PDFs — kept local to avoid bulk-republishing real people's names in a
#   searchable public repo. Spec §5/§13 calls for null/hashed bidder labels
#   in any republished form.
data/probe/
data/raw/
data/enrichment/

# Claude Code workspace state
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/worktrees/
.agents/
